data.description: Discover tranquility at 18357 Andy Hill Rd, a two-story home on 21.10 acres in Lakeview, Oregon. Ideal for those seeking privacy and a self-sufficient lifestyle, this property offers spacious family living in a serene setting. Highlights: Hidden Away and Self-Sufficient: Set on 21.10 acres with a backup generator and water filtration system, perfect for discreet living. Spacious Residence: A 2,421 sq ft two-story home designed for comfort and practicality. Versatile Outbuildings: Includes a general-purpose building, pump house, and sheds for various uses. Family-Friendly: Ample outdoor space for family, pets, and projects, supported by the Lakeview School District. Additional Features: A large garage adds to the home's functionality. Experience Rural Charm and Comfort: This property is an ideal blend of rural peace and modern amenities. Schedule your visit to see the potential of this unique estate.
